programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep24
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam keluar wad serta di terima baik ibu Sheila. Sheila meminta Nizam bersabar kerana dia perlu memantau kesihatan dan menyambung urusan kerja perniagaan bapanya. Semasa berkereta, Sheila ternampak Hani bersama Shariff dan mengambil gambar. Sheila tidak tahu menahu Shariff terpaksa mencari dan menemui Hani kerana ingin memberitahu dan menyampaikan hasil siasatan DNA bahawa mereka dua beradik. Hani masih sangsi dan mengarapkan pengesahan lagi. Shariff pula terpaksa bergegas berkaitan siasatan skandal Dato Fuad dan Suraya dan Hani ingin membantunya dituruti Kalsom (penyiasat upahan Shariff). Sheila pula memajukan gambar itu kepada Nizam agar jangan lagi mengharap Hani. Terdahulu Mizan meluahkan rasa hatinya kepada Dzul, dia ingin berhenti kerja berikutan sikap isterinya yang berbaik dengan Shariff. Semasa Shariff, Hani dan Kalsom tiba di bawah bangunan di mana Dato Fuad dan Suraya berada, bapa Shariff juga tiba dan dia terus bersama penguatkuasa Jabatan Ugama semasa Dato Fuad dan Suraya ditahan. Kemudiannya ketika Datin Umairah bersama Shariff, bapa Shariff (abang datin Umairah), Hani dan kalsom berbincang, Datin Umairah menerangkan usaha yang dibuatnya sehingga dapat tahu status Hani. Sebaliknya bapa Shariff menyarankan selidiki lagi. Hani merayu dan berharap jangan sama sekali anggapkan dia ingin mengambil kesempatan.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep26
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila sangat mengharapkan Hani dapat berhubung dengan Nizam kerana Hani sahaja yang akan dilayan panggilan. Hani menelefon Nizam semata-mata kerana harapan Sheila, merayu dia pulang. Sheila berharap dia dapat meminta maaf akibat kesalahannya. Kesempatan Hani berbual, Nizam sering memujuk Hani, menyuarakan segala perasaan dan janji mereka dahulu. Malahan Mizan dengan berkeras hati menyatakan cintanya hanya Hani, bagi Sheila dia tidak sesekali akan memaafkannya. Apabila Hani menyatakan kesetiaan hanyalah kepada suaminya. Nizam sekali lagi bertegas yang dia akan menentukan Mizan tidak menyentuhnya. Hani walau pun seperti berbelah bagi, tetapi dia seorang yang cekal dan tetap taat kepada suaminya. Di sebelah malamnya, Hani terbawa-bawa bagaimana kisah mereka berdua bercinta dahulu. Malahan di satu taman, pernah mereka sama-sama meletakkan "kunci cinta" mereka sebagai janji seia sekata. Suraya masih dengan rakan lelaki yang cuba mencari kerja untuk dia menjadi "modelling". Apa pun melalui jalan pintas Suraya juga bersetuju menjadi pelacur berkelas melalui seorang ahli perniagaan berbangsa Cina. Mizan tidak berapa sihat, kebetulan Hani telah pulang ke rumah. Hani menjagai Mizan dengan sebaiknya. Mizan juga mahukan Hani memanggil dirinya "abang", yang menjadi Hani terasa berlainan. Mereka juga mula keluar bersekali bersantai.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep28
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam seolah akur nasihat Mizan dia berubah dari sikap lama. Pertemuan dan perbincangannya dengan Sheila, Nizam mengharap Sheila menerimanya sebagaimana mereka pernah bersama dan berjanji ketika sama menuntut di luar negara dulu. Penyatuan mereka cukup menyenangkan ibu Sheila dan mereka juga berkurus untuk menunaikan Ibadah Umrah. Hani bercadang dengan Mizan untuk menemui keluarga Yusri. Mizan setuju tapi merahsiakan yang Yusri dan keluarganya telah pun ada di rumah Dato Omar (bapa Hani) disediakan untuk arwah ibu Hani. Setibanya Mizan dan Hani membuatkan Hani kehairanan. Kejutan bagi Hani, mendapati keluarga Yusri ada bersama Dato Omar. Turut ada Syariff di samping Nizam dan Sheila. Dato Omar menerangkan rumah mereka berada amat bernilai baginya, apakan daya ibu Hani meninggal, lalu memutus dengan menyerahkan kepada Hani. Hani dan Mizan yang telah ada rumah bersetuju agar keluarga Yusri tinggal di situ. Dato Omar juga memaklumkan yang Syariff akan berkahwin dengan Kalsom. Dalam masa yang sama Mizan menerima panggilan telefon daripada Suraya dalam keadaan nazak, memohon maaf dan sempat mengucap dua kalimah sahadah sebelum meninggal dunia. Sebelum itu Suraya membunuh Ah Meng. Diakhirnya pasangan Nizam dan Sheila menemui pasangan Mizan dan Hani dalam suasana kekeluargaan. Nizam memohon maaf kepada Hani di atas segala tingkahlakunya. Mizan pula terlebih awal memaafkan Nizam

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep24
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam keluar wad serta di terima baik ibu Sheila. Sheila meminta Nizam bersabar kerana dia perlu memantau kesihatan dan menyambung urusan kerja perniagaan bapanya. Semasa berkereta, Sheila ternampak Hani bersama Shariff dan mengambil gambar. Sheila tidak tahu menahu Shariff terpaksa mencari dan menemui Hani kerana ingin memberitahu dan menyampaikan hasil siasatan DNA bahawa mereka dua beradik. Hani masih sangsi dan mengarapkan pengesahan lagi. Shariff pula terpaksa bergegas berkaitan siasatan skandal Dato Fuad dan Suraya dan Hani ingin membantunya dituruti Kalsom (penyiasat upahan Shariff). Sheila pula memajukan gambar itu kepada Nizam agar jangan lagi mengharap Hani. Terdahulu Mizan meluahkan rasa hatinya kepada Dzul, dia ingin berhenti kerja berikutan sikap isterinya yang berbaik dengan Shariff. Semasa Shariff, Hani dan Kalsom tiba di bawah bangunan di mana Dato Fuad dan Suraya berada, bapa Shariff juga tiba dan dia terus bersama penguatkuasa Jabatan Ugama semasa Dato Fuad dan Suraya ditahan. Kemudiannya ketika Datin Umairah bersama Shariff, bapa Shariff (abang datin Umairah), Hani dan kalsom berbincang, Datin Umairah menerangkan usaha yang dibuatnya sehingga dapat tahu status Hani. Sebaliknya bapa Shariff menyarankan selidiki lagi. Hani merayu dan berharap jangan sama sekali anggapkan dia ingin mengambil kesempatan.

programme.desc: Nasib baik sekuriti kondo bantu Suzan. Disebabkan tak nak Aidid ambil tindakan, Sherry ketemu Haryati dan Aidid lalu minta selesaikan hal ni. Aidid janji lepaskan Juliana asalkan Juliana tak muncul lagi depan Aidid dan Suzan. Haryati yang malu, bawa diri lalu kenal dengan sorang ahli NGO bernama Ustazah Ummi Fikrah. Haryati rasa Ummi Fikrah pelik. Suatu malam, Haryati sakit. Lalu Ummi Fikrah bawa Haryati balik rumahnya dan Haryati selesa dan nak tinggal situ. Sebab risau juga, Aidid dan Suzan muncul cari Haryati di rumah Ummi Fikrah. Haryati nampak tak senang.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep21
programme.desc: Aidid tak selesa dengan keprihatinan Zafuan terhadap Suzan walaupun dia tahu Suzan sakit perut. Suzan minta maaf sebab ambil ubat sesuka hati semata-mata nak hamil. Aidid minta dia sabar dan tunggu rezeki Tuhan. Fara balik dari Izmir sebab ibunya disahkan kanser. Dia cuti satu semester untuk jaga ibunya. Fara yang makin rapat hubungan dengan Zafuan, merasakan Zafuan lebih banyak beri perhatian pada Suzan. Haryati pula masih kurang senang dengan hubungan Suzan-Zafuan lalu minta Aidid berhati-hati. programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep22

Marissa daring dan cuba ambil kesempatan pada Aidid. Suzan rasa tak senang dengan kehadiran Marissa. Dia bagi amaran keras setiap kali Marissa cuba buat sesuatu pada Aidid. Fara akhirnya kesal sebab salah sangka pada Zafuan. Suatu malam, Suzan bimbang sebab Aidid tak balik lagi, lalu pergi pejabat. Alangkah terkejutnya dia bila lihat Marissa sedang picit kepala Aidid dan nampak mesra.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep9
programme.desc: Episod – 9 memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal memikirkan cara terbaik untuk menyimpan rahsia tentang batu permata daripada Hariman tanpa menyedari Hariman telah mengetahui batu-batu permata yang dicari selama ini berada dalam simpanan mereka. Imran juga mula mengesyaki bahawa berkemungkinan Hariman adalah salah seorang perompak yang sedang mencari batu-batu permata tersebut. Sementara itu Maira berjaya memujuk ibunya yang kebetulan pulang ke kampung untuk menempah seutas loket bertatahkan sebutir batu milikinya. Dengan perasaan begitu teruja Ibu Maira bergegas pulang semula ke kampung untuk bertemu Maira setelah pemilik sebuah kedai emas bahawa batu milik Maira yang disangka tidak berharga adalah permata asli bernilai belasan ribu ringgit.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Bisma, seorang remaja yang mempunyai bakat seni mempertahankan diri semula jadi menyukai Bella, seorang gadis di kolejnya. Tetapi teman lelakinya, Attar sentiasa mengganggu Bisma sehingga seorang lelaki misteri melatihnya untuk melawan.

programme.title: The Sacred Riana: Beginning
programme.desc: Pada zaman kanak-kanaknya, Riana tinggal di sebuah bandar kecil bersama bapanya dan ibunya yang menjalankan perniagaan rumah pengebumian. Musibah memerlukan mereka berpindah ke rumah Pakcik Johan di Jakarta dan Riana bertemu dengan anak patung Riani. Riana semakin dewasa dan suatu hari telah dilawati oleh Puan Klara, seorang guru kaunselor di sekolahnya yang ingin mengetahui sebab Riana tidak hadir ke sekolah dan mencadangkan Riana untuk dipulihkan. Musibah menimpa ibu bapa Riana. Puan Klara datang lagi bersama Hendro, Lusi dan Anggi, untuk membantu Riana beramah mesra. Tetapi, kehadiran mereka mencetuskan masalah yang lebih besar; makhluk ganas masa lalu ia melepaskan dan mengganas mereka semua.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep3/04
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Samson
programme.desc: Selepas kehilangan cinta dalam hidupnya kepada seorang Putera Filistin yang kejam, seorang pemuda Ibrani dengan kekuatan ghaib membela rakyatnya, mengorbankan segala-galanya untuk membalas cintanya, umatnya, dan Tuhan.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep2
programme.desc: EP. 2 mengisahkan Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep4
programme.desc: Akil yang berada di rumahnya telah didatangi 4 lembaga yang menyerupai hantu yang Akil gelar sebagai Kim Chi, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Jendul. Ke empat mereka mempunyai masalah masing-masing dan datang cuba mendapat pertolongan Akil yang dianggap boleh membantu menyelesaikan masalah mereka dengan pertolongan cincin 4 keramat yang dimiliki oleh Akil. Bagi permulaannya mereka sepakat supaya masalah Jendul diselesaikan dahulu. Jendul pada suatu masa dulu berkawan baik dengan seorang budak lelaki bernama Akmal. Akmal kadang-kadang bergurau dengan Jendul dan gelak ketawa. Ibu bapa Akmal berasa pelik kerana mereka tidak nampak kewujudan Jendul. Ibu bapa Akmal minta Tok Misai mengubati Akmal. Jendul dapat dikuasai oleh Tok Misai dan sekarang Jendul mahu Akil membebaskan dia daripada dikuasai Tok Misai. Akil bersetuju dan pergi ke rumah ibubapa Akmal berpura-pura mencari kerja sebagai pemotong rumput.

programme.title: The Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang pengawal peribadi yang malang dipecat oleh anak pelanggannya kerana kematian bapa pelanggannya. Anak lelaki itu kemudian diburu oleh pembunuh upahan yang tidak mahu dia mewarisi syarikat bapanya.

programme.title: Plan B Ep10
programme.desc: Episod ke-10 ini mengisahkan Khai, Iris, Mika dan Que terlibat dalam satu rompakan. Mereka merompak sebuah van syarikat keselamatan milik bapa Mika, Yusof, yang membawa sejumlah wang besar. Mereka bertembung dengan kumpulan yang diketuai oleh King. Dalam aksi tembak menembak antara kedua-dua kumpulan, kesemua pengawal keselamatan yang mengiringi wang itu, ditembak mati oleh King. Mika juga cedera ditembak. Dalam aksi kejar mengejar antara dua kumpulan itu dan tembak menembak, King dan orang-orangnya mati ditembak oleh Khai, ketika berjaya membawa lari wang rompakan itu. Di pejabat keselamatan, Yusof dapat menyaksi aksi rompakan itu melalui kamera tertutup dan mendapati anaknya, Mika ditembak.

programme.title: The Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang pengawal peribadi yang malang dipecat oleh anak pelanggannya kerana kematian bapa pelanggannya. Anak lelaki itu kemudian diburu oleh pembunuh upahan yang tidak mahu dia mewarisi syarikat bapanya.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Ep.6 mengisahkan Haris, pengganti Rafiq, dijumpai mati akibat kemalangan di jalan raya. Kerana ini, Rafiq tidak perlu berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur. Dina yang menyerupai Sarakit dapat juga melihat apa Sarakit lalui seperti semasa Sarakit dirogol dan mempunyai perasaan benci terhadap Pak Bado. Pak Bado terus diganggu suara bayi menangis dan menjumpai janin di kebunnya. Sementara itu, Tat, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, mulai diganggu hantu tenggek sehingga dia tidak berani keluar malam. Ramdi berjumpa Tat untuk mengajaknya berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur kerana tidak mahu mereka mati sia-sia seperti yang berlaku pada Kiol. Tat keberatan tetapi Ramdi bersedia membawanya keluar dari kampung apabila perlu.

programme.desc: 0Apabila kepala patung yang suci di sebuah kampung dicuri, seorang ahli seni mempertahankan diri pergi ke bandar besar dan mendapati dirinya mengambil dunia bawah tanah untuk mendapatkannya.

programme.title: Raging Pheonix
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penjahat menculik dan membunuh wanita di sekitar Thailand. Sanim dan rakan-rakannya, setelah orang tersayang diculik, telah bergabung untuk memecahkan kumpulan penculik. Dalam percubaan penculikan yang gagal, Deu telah diselamatkan oleh anak kapal Sanim. Selepas mempelajari gaya seni mempertahankan diri mereka yang unik, Deu membantu memikat kumpulan itu ke dalam pertempuran epik untuk menyelamatkan wanita di seluruh Thailand.

programme.title: The Sacred Riana: Beginning

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan sedang Daniel, Shah dan Adam bersedia di perkarangan perumahan. Tiba-tiba seorang suri rumah bergegas datang melaporkan di dapurnya ada lembaga lilin. Mereka bertiga ke situ, lembaga kuali menyerang mereka, sehingga Daniel jatuh dan cedera dan perlu rawatan di wad. Bad datang memberi sedikit wang sagu hati selain memberi jaminan pihak insuran akan mengurus lanjut. Nur terus melakukan misi untuk bapa dan ibunya berbaik-baik. Kedua pihak kelihatan positif. programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep16
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Danial terpaksa menyelamatkan Yasmin dari tawanan Hakim. Hakim mengalami halunisasi akibat telah lama tidak mengambil ubat psikiatrik. Dato’ Bakri bapa kepada Yasmin dan Datin Rosnah ibu kepada Hakim akan berkahwin. Dalam kes berasingan, Mazlan telah ditangkap oleh orang-orang bodyguard Farish. Dia diberi amaran supaya tidak memaparkan gambar bogel Kasandra. Mazlan diberhentikan kerja sebagai Pengurus Kasandra. Eisha sepupu kepada Farish, meminta pertolongan ibu Farish memujuk supaya Farish bersetuju berkahwin dengannya. Akibatnya perhubungan Farish dengan Nasha menghadapi masalah. Bakri bodyguard Eira pulang ke kampung. Eira terpikat dengan Azlan, Sebaliknya Mak Mah terpikat dengan Bakri untuk dijodohkan dengan Eira. Dalam kes baru, Ryan bodyguard kepada seorang Dato’ menghadapi masalah dengan seorang perempuan simpanan.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Ep.6 mengisahkan Haris, pengganti Rafiq, dijumpai mati akibat kemalangan di jalan raya. Kerana ini, Rafiq tidak perlu berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur. Sementara itu, Tat, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, mulai diganggu hantu tenggek sehingga dia tidak berani keluar malam. Ramdi berjumpa Tat untuk mengajaknya berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur kerana tidak mahu mereka mati sia-sia seperti yang berlaku pada Kiol. Tat keberatan tetapi Ramdi bersedia membawanya keluar dari kampung apabila perlu.

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep17
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nasha melarikan diri kerana tidak dapat menerima kenyataan Dato' Amir dan Mak Jah adalah ibu bapa kandungnya. Farish akhirnya berjumpa Nasha, dia memujuknya menerima kenyataan sebenar. Nasha kemudiannya menerima hakikat tersebut. Farish juga berjaya memujuk ibu dan bapanya menerima Nasha sebagai menantu mereka. Danial masih menjadi bodyguard Eliza, dia berjanji akan menjaga Eliza seperti diamanahkan. Rashid telah diberitahu oleh ibunya, dia dan Eliza sebenarnya adalah adik-beradik. Rashid kemudiannya dimanahkan untuk menguruskan syarikat Dato' Zaidi. Rahul pula sebagai bodyguard Maya berjaya mengesan Boboy yang telah menghilangkan diri. Maya berjanji akan menjadi ibu yang terbaik, dia bersama-sama dengan Mikhail dan Zulaikha akan memberipenjagaan kepada Boboy.

programme.title: Gangster
programme.desc: Berdasarkan geng-geng Bangkok yang terkenal pada tahun 1950-an-60an. Kisah ini mengikuti seorang banduan yang baru dibebaskan yang ingin hidup lurus, tetapi tidak mengetahui apa-apa selain kehidupan seorang samseng, dia kembali kepada kumpulan lamanya.

programme.title: Talak
programme.desc: Johan dan Liza sering bertengkar sehingga membawa kepada penceraian. Tetapi setiap kali ianya terjadi, mereka akan merujuk kembali. Tanpa disedari, Johan telah pun melafazkan talak kepada Liza sebanyak tiga kali, ini menyebabkan mereka tidak boleh merujuk kembali. Johan terpaksa mencari lelaki yang boleh dipercayai untuk berkahwin dengan Liza supaya mereka boleh kembali bersama. Namun, malang menimpa apabila lelaki untuk tidak mahu melepaskan Liza.

programme.title: Konstabel Mamat
programme.desc: Akibat kelalaian dalam operasi menangkap ketua gengster iaitu Mail Musang yang merupakan bapa ayam sindiket pelacuran di Kuala Lumpur, Mamat digantung tugas selama tiga bulan. Meskipun digantung, Mamat tetap rajin dan menjalankan tugas menangkap penjenayah. Mamat yang jatuh cinta dengan kekasih gelap kepada Mail Musang telah diketahui olehnya. Kejadian ini telah membawa kepada penangkapan Mail dan Mamat tidak lagi digantung tugas.

programme.title: Sikit Punya Gila
programme.desc: Hamid dan Dharma keluar merantau mencari kekayaan di bandar bertemu Nora dan Norlia. Hamid, penjual jagung rebus dan Dharma, penjaga lif tinggal di rumah milik pasangan suami isteri dan berjiran bersama Nora dan Norlia. Kerana ingin mencari kekayaan dengan menggunakan jalan mudah, pelbagai kesusahan terpaksa dihadapi oleh mereka berdua.

programme.title: Ragam Pemandu
programme.desc: Pemandu yang setia dan tidak pernah mengeluh, Hamid tidak disukai oleh isteri tuannya, Rubiah. Tuannya, Rahim pula seorang yang baik hati dan sukakan Hamid. Dia sering membantu membiayai pelajaran anak-anak Hamid dan menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi olehnya. Satu pertengkaran menyebabkan Hamid berhenti kerja namun Rahim tampil membantu mengambilnya bekerja di syarikat insurans miliknya.

programme.title: Adik Manja
programme.desc: Guru lelaki pertama di sekolah berasrama penuh perempuan terpaksa menyembunyikan satu rahsia besar apabila terpaksa membawa pulang seorang bayi lelaki. Pelbagai helah terpaksa digunakannya namun diketahui juga oleh pelajar-pelajar institusi itu. Pelajar-pelajar tersebut mengambil keputusan untuk membantunya bersama seorang lagi guru di situ.

programme.title: Panglima Badol
programme.desc: Badol ingin keluar merantau mencari pengalaman hidup seperti apa yang dilakukan bapanya. Ditentang ibunya namun direlakan dengan satu syarat - tidak boleh mengambil tahu perihal orang lain. Setibanya di sebuah pulau, kekecohan berlaku apabila Maya Sari, anak angkat Datuk Tumpang dilarikan konco Datuk Panglima Wira. Badol secara tidak sengaja berjaya menyelamatkan Maya Sari dan diberi gelaran Panglima Badol.

programme.title: Tak Ori Tapi Ok
programme.desc: Keinginan seorang pengarah filem yang ingin menghasilkan naskhah baru. Yassin mahu melakukan kemunculan semula setelah sekian lama menemui jalan buntu dalam kerjayanya. Menemui seseorang yang mahu membiayai projek terbarunya, dia pun mula mencari pelakon-pelakon untuk membintanginya. Pelbagai rintangan dihadapinya dalam mencari pelakon yang boleh meniru gaya seperti P.Ramlee.

programme.title: Guru Badul
programme.desc: Badul diambil bekerja di pejabat Hj. Lamin sebagai seorang pengutip hutang. Badul sebenarnya berpura-pura menjadi orang alim membuatkan Hj. Lamin sangat tertarik akan perwatakannya itu. Dia banyak mempelajari ilmu agama dengan Badul dan ingin menjadikannya sebagai seorang menantu. Namun satu insiden telah memecahkan rahsianya apabila Hj. Lamin terlihat Badul sedang menari-nari.

programme.title: Salah Bapak
programme.desc: Jamil dan Osman terpaksa melalui pelbagai rintangan untuk menuntut hak mereka ke atas harta peninggalan Al-Sagof, bapa mereka yang telah meninggal dunia. Pak Joko ingin cuba membolot harta Al-Sagof lalu merancang pelbagai taktik kotor untuk mendapatkannya. Seroja, gadis yang menyewa tapak tanak bapa mereka untuk membuka warung turut terlibat apabila dia digunakan Pak Joko.

Lamin terlihat Badul sedang menari-nari.

programme.title: Kemarau Cinta

Ingin cuba melakukan perubahan demi kemajuan di kampung namun tidak semua bersetuju dengan perubahan yang dibawa olehnya. Pelbagai halangan perlu ditempuhinya namun dia bersikap pantang berundur sebelum berjuang.

programme.desc: Seorang wartawan muda, Hafiz ingin membantu kekasihnya, Ruby. Ruby bergelut untuk mengatasi trauma dan pengalaman buruk dari zaman kecilnya. Hafiz sedang menulis rencana tentang kisah Pak Arif yang memiliki tanah pusaka di kampung. Hashim pula ingin membeli kesemua tanah miliknya dan menggunakan taktik jahat untuk mendapatkannya. Ternyata, Ruby adalah anak saudara kepada Pak Arif.

programme.title: Salah Bapak

Pak Joko ingin cuba membolot harta Al-Sagof lalu merancang pelbagai taktik kotor untuk mendapatkannya. Seroja, gadis yang menyewa tapak tanak bapa mereka untuk membuka warung turut terlibat apabila dia digunakan Pak Joko.

programme.title: Ragam Pemandu

Dia sering membantu membiayai pelajaran anak-anak Hamid dan menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi olehnya. Satu pertengkaran menyebabkan Hamid berhenti kerja namun Rahim tampil membantu mengambilnya bekerja di syarikat insurans miliknya.

Menemui seseorang yang mahu membiayai projek terbarunya, dia pun mula mencari pelakon-pelakon untuk membintanginya. Meskipun digantung, Mamat tetap rajin dan menjalankan tugas menangkap penjenayah. Mamat yang jatuh cinta dengan kekasih gelap kepada Mail Musang telah diketahui olehnya. programme.title: In the Family (T) Ep1112
programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.title: Battle Tour(M) Ep2
programme.desc: Brand new concept of a travelogue show! Hosts will be using a different perspectives and knowledge to show you the latest tourist spots to check in!

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep837838
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep673
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep450
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Young Days No Fears(M) Ep4041
programme.desc: The six girls, as good friends, have gone through their difficulties and crises in relationship, at work, and in their marriage together. Despite many challenges in life, they are not afraid. They have got each other’s back.

programme.title: She's a Man. He's a Woman.
programme.desc: This is a romantic comedy about a quarrelsome and loving couple whose spirits are being swapped over after a thunderstorm. The sexy lady finds herself carrying an ugly man’s spirit, and vice versa. Can they switch their spirits back, or do they need to get use to the situation for the rest of their lives?

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Monster Hunt
programme.desc: The pregnant queen of the monster realm flees a civil war and lands in human world, near Yung Ning Village. She seeks the help of a wimpy villager to become the surrogate father for her child, Wuba. From the time he was born, little Wuba embarks on a thrilling journey to escape from those who want to capture him at all costs.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Ip Man
programme.desc: Wing Chun grandmaster Ip Man’s matchless fighting skills are revered all over China. Set during the Sino-Japanese War, Ip Man is forced to leave his home and work to support his family. With only his martial arts skills, he reluctantly agrees to train others in the art of Wing Chun for self-defense.

programme.title: From Beijing With Love
programme.desc: Stephen Chow writes, directs & stars in this hilarious James Bond spoof that sees the Chinese government assign their worst secret agent (Chow) to recover a stolen dinosaur skull.

programme.title: Mr. Long
programme.desc: A Taiwanese hitman Mr. Long escapes from the triad after his assignment in Tokyo gone awry. He encounters a Taiwanese woman and her son and the three of them start a new life together. Unfortunately, Mr. Long is being pursued by the triad again…

programme.title: Hail the Judge
programme.desc: A low level magistrate is run out of town for defending a beautiful murder suspect. Through a series of comedic events he ascends to the top rank & returns looking for revenge.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: 12 Golden Ducks
programme.desc: This is a comeback story about the misadventures of a group of gigolos, led by Future, trying to make their mark in Hong Kong. As with any profession, they have their share of setbacks, but their ability to find laughter within the tears reflects the drive, passion and the indomitable spirit of the Hong Kong people.

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chef’s delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Nezha
programme.desc: A former top team racing driver wants to prove himself in a race but accidentally hurts his teammate Lily, leading to the team’s downfall. When an inexperienced virtual car racing champion joins the team and unexpectedly shines in a real-life race, can the three drivers team up to regain glory for their team?

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return…

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fiancé left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his family’s massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quin’s trust, Nick becomes his protégé and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Finding Mr. Right
programme.desc: A woman from Beijing, pregnant with the child of her rich married boyfriend, flies to Seattle in order to deliver the baby. She meets a Chinese immigrant man working as a driver there, and as she starts to learn more about him, her life begins to change.

programme.title: Push and Shove
programme.desc: A puppy gets gravely injured while defending them from the neighbor's large and aggressive Tibetan Mastiff. The arrogant owner of the Tibetan Mastiff, however, refuses to take responsibility, and the police aren't of much help since no people were hurt. When push comes to shove, the puppy’s owner vows to fight for justice for his dog.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her father’s death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late father’s hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protégé Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Bio Raiders
programme.desc: Famed doctor Mo Tian Shi (Richard Ng) concocts an immortality medicine to save his terminally ill daughter Xiao Xin, but the cost for immortality is that she must drink human blood. Twenty years later, Mo's apprentice Li Yao Shi (Chin Siu Ho) returns to town and notices something is amiss, only to realise the horror is just about to begin…

programme.title: The Magnificent Swordsman
programme.desc: The Magnificent Swordsman centres on the hero who vows vengeance against evil bandits who killed his family when he was a child. The hero recruits several friends to help the peasants rid their village of marauding bandits, the leader of the band being the man who killed his family.

programme.title: The Crimson Palm
programme.desc: A poor student, Lin, is engaged to the daughter of a rich man who despises Lin because of his family’s declining status. Lin visits his fiancée before he leaves for the imperial examination, but finds a maid lying dead in blood. As Lin’s bloody handprint is left on the site, he is accused of the murder. How can Justice Bao prove his innocence?

programme.title: Long Road To Gallantry
programme.desc: Tu Meng Fei makes his way to the world after completing his kung fu training. En route, he rescues Mu Wan Erh and Li San Nan from a band of thugs and later learnt of a 20-year conflict between the evil Thunder Gang Chief Leng Tian Lei and the Dragon Sect. Mu’s lost father is none other than the Thunder Gang Chief, who also killed Li’s father…

programme.title: Masked Avengers
programme.desc: The "godfather of the kung-fu film," Chang Cheh, started a winning streak by making the internationally renowned THE FIVE VENOMS. He followed that hit with many more high-flying "bloody good" entertainments featuring the same cast in new roles. But of all the "Venom" movies, this one stands out as perhaps the most chilling. Masked killers are wreaking havoc and instilling terror with their vicious weapons of choice: razor-sharp, gut-shattering tridents. Only three fearless fighters dare investigate, leading to mass murder and magnificent martial arts. Chien Hsiao-hou, future co-star of Yuen Woo-ping's THE TAI-CHI MASTER joins the trio to get tri-pierced. The core "Venoms" themselves handle the intricate, always impressive, sometimes awe-inspiring, choreography in this unforgettable exercise in "grand guignol kung-fu."

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a police’s son, blames his father for his mother’s death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: Tales Of A Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu Chia-hui, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Invincible Enforcer
programme.desc: A young man is at the wrong place at the wrong time. As he offends a police inspector, he is thrown into jail and even when released, the police goes after him until he has no choice but to become a real criminal. Only a kind and beautiful probation officer is on his side, but can she help him?

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature. His first official business is to inspect the brothels and take the prostitutes home to become his concubines. Feng is finally killed by his officers, but will the new general rule the city differently?

programme.title: Ten Tigers Of Kwang Tung
programme.desc: The Ten Tigers of Kwang Tung is a group of anti-Ching martial artists who have killed a Ching official. Years later, when five disciples and descendants of Ten Tigers meet one night, one of them is killed by the son of the late Ching official who returns with a vengeance. They must fight against him to protect the Ten Tigers clan…

programme.title: Black Magic
programme.desc: Hsu Lo is up against an evil black magic practitioner San Kan Mi, who wants to place a death spell on him and a love spell on his fiancée Wang Chu Ying. Fortunately, Wang's friends manage to find another veteran witch doctor to take on the evil San. This bone-chilling tale of good versus evil races to a heart-stopping ending.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demon’s clutches.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends’ help.

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor and action choreographer, the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sister’s wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman. After the marriage mismatches are revealed, the lovers and their families are taken to court, where Prefecture Chief Qiao manages to work out a happy ending.

programme.title: Five Elements Ninjas
programme.desc: The film is about a Chinese martial arts school finds itself outclassed by their rivals, they hire elite ninja from Japan to destroy the school. The lone survivor of the massacre learns the secrets of ninjutsu and seeks revenge against the ninja.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: Return Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: One of Shaw Studio’s highest grossing movies ever, this is the story of Li Chin Huan, the renowned, charming and sentimental swordsman who must fight many opponents, including an evil Clan Chief, for a place in the martial arts world.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: The Silver Fox
programme.desc: The formidable swordswoman Silver Fox was a child when her father was senselessly wounded by his step brother, and her mother raped. It is payback time eighteen years later, as her father trains her up with kung fu to take revenge on his behalf.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: Oath Of Death
programme.desc: Three Sung loyalists become blood brothers to fight the tyranny of the Tartar invaders. To oust the oppressors altogether, Ma releases the kidnapped Tartar princess in a strategic effort to gain points with the invaders, but it soon becomes apparent that he desires both a great position and power, and will do anything to get it…

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: The Master
programme.desc: Gao Jian is the disciple of the martial arts master Shi but is constantly being punished by his master for no reason. One day, Gao accidentally saves his master’s rival Jin, so Jin teaches him his unique martial arts skill in return. However, Master Shi sees this as Gao’s betrayal…

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charn’s beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dong’s concubine as he knows Dong’s adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: The Deadly Breaking Sword
programme.desc: Warrior Tuan Chang Qing meets courtesan Liu Yin Xi in a small town. Liu pleads Tuan to kill the underworld master Guo Tian Sheng, known as the "Killer Doctor", in order to avenge the death of her fiance. Tuan and gambling addict Xiao Dao breaks into Guo's household, triggering the battle of good against evil.

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: The Black Lizard
programme.desc: Young swordsman Lung Fei encounters strange omens portending the death of his fiancé. His enquiries with the help of Chief Constable Tieh Hu reveal an astounding story, in this tale of men and women struggling to save their true loves.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobra’s blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his father’s old rival.

programme.title: The Story Of Sue San
programme.desc: TIn this Huangmei Opera romance, Wang is the son of a respected government official whereas Sue San is a famous prostitute. Although they love each other and seem to be perfectly matched, the two are worlds apart when it comes to social ranking, which will prove hard to overcome...

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan (Chang Chan-peng) is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai (Alexander Fu Sheng). The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific (Nat Chen Pai-chiang). Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou (Wang Yu).

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Dragon Missile
programme.desc: Sima works for a corrupt lord Qin who is suffering from a deadly disease that only a special herb can cure. Qin sends him on an urgent mission to retrieve it, but the task is made more difficult when Sima has to fight off other martial artists who want to steal the cure away from him. He has to fight with his ultimate weapon, the Dragon Missile!

programme.title: 2023 Shark Grand Prix de France Highlights
programme.desc: Highlights - The French city and circuit of Le Mans are synonymous with motorsport - having hosted two and four wheel races and endurance events for many years. Le Mans first held a motorcycle Grand Prix event in 1969, when the great Giacomo Agostini won the 500cc race, lapping all the other riders on his MV Agusta. The modern circuit has been a permanent fixture on the MotoGP™ calendar since 2000. Local French fans are knowledgeable and passionate about their racing, with a boisterous atmosphere at races. French riders of different eras and in different classes such as Johann Zarco, Christian Sarron, Olivier Jacque, Arnaud Vincent, Guy Bertin, Randy de Puniet and Mike Di Meglio have brought their country race wins and titles, adding to France’s significant racing heritage.

programme.title: UFC Fight Night: Kara France vs Albazi
programme.desc: Prelims - Rapidly becoming the most exciting division in the UFC, the flyweight class will take center stage on June 3, when Kai Kara-France and Amir Albazi face off in a five-round UFC Fight Night main event at the APEX in Las Vegas. programme.desc: ROAD TO UFC Season 2 is the most significant opportunity for Asia's top MMA prospects to make it to the world stage. The opening round is divided into four episodes, each of which includes four tournament bouts and one additional non-tournament bout. The event will be held in front of a live audience and the episodes will be produced and distributed for live broadcast using Remote Integration Model production (REMI) from UFC’s state-of-the-art Broadcast Operations Center (BOC) at UFC Apex in Las Vegas in the USA. programme.title: LIVE: UFC 289: Nunes vs. Aldana
programme.desc: Prelims - In a year of excellence, Mexico may see its fourth world champion crowned. In the UFC’s return to Canada on June 10, Guadalajara’s Irene Aldana challenges Brazil’s Amanda Nunes for the UFC bantamweight title in the main event of UFC 289 at Vancouver’s Rogers Arena. Last July, the “Lioness” evened the score with Julianna Pena, regaining her title and setting up a meeting with Aldana, whose fight-altering power has led her to wins over Macy Chiasson, Yana Santos and Ketlen Vieira. Plus, in the co-main event, it’s a pivotal clash in the lightweight division when former champ Charles Oliveira battles surging contender Beneil Dariush
